Class AdminEventHandlerTest

java.lang.Object
AdminEventHandlerTest
public class AdminEventHandlerTest
extends java.lang.Object
A test class for the EventHandler class with admin privileges. This class establishes a connection to the Mock Database and tests actions in EventHandler that only administrators can perform.
